[{"title":"Manjaro安装配置KDE桌面","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Linux/manjaro configure kde desktop.html","content":"<h2 id=\"系统更新与升级\"><a href=\"#系统更新与升级\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"系统更新与升级\"></a>系统更新与升级</h2><p>1.排列源：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo pacman-mirrors -g</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>2.然后同步：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo pacman-optimize&amp;&amp; sync</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>3.升级系统：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo pacman -Syyu</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h2 id=\"基本软件配置\"><a href=\"#基本软件配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基本软件配置\"></a>基本软件配置</h2><p>1.安装fcitx<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S fcitx fcitx-im</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>2.安装Python3-pip<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div><div class=\"line\">2</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">curl -O https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py</div><div class=\"line\">python3 get-pip.py</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>3.安装Virtualbox<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div><div class=\"line\">2</div><div class=\"line\">3</div><div class=\"line\">4</div><div class=\"line\">5</div><div class=\"line\">6</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S virtualbox</div><div class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S linux-headers</div><div class=\"line\">sudo usermod -a -G vboxusers $USER</div><div class=\"line\">group $USER</div><div class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S virtualbox-guest-utils</div><div class=\"line\">sudo /sbin/rcvboxdrv setup</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h2 id=\"搭建Hexo博客\"><a href=\"#搭建Hexo博客\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"搭建Hexo博客\"></a>搭建Hexo博客</h2><p>1.安装nvm（Node Version Manager）</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/v0.33.1/install.sh | bash</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>之后重新打开终端</p>\n<p>2.安装nodejs和npm</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">nvm stable</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>3.安装hexo<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">npm install -g hexo-cli</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h2 id=\"安装Chromium-Flash-Plugin\"><a href=\"#安装Chromium-Flash-Plugin\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Chromium Flash Plugin\"></a>安装Chromium Flash Plugin</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S pepper-flash</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>参考链接：<a href=\"http://www.cnblogs.com/vanwoos/p/5470604.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">http://www.cnblogs.com/vanwoos/p/5470604.html</a></p>\n","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["hexo","Manjaro"]},{"title":"python猜数字游戏","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Python/python猜数字游戏.html","content":"<h2 id=\"guessNumber-py\"><a href=\"#guessNumber-py\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"guessNumber.py\"></a>guessNumber.py</h2><figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">from</span> random <span class=\"keyword\">import</span> randint</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">num = randint(<span class=\"number\">1</span>, <span class=\"number\">100</span>)</div><div class=\"line\">bingo = <span class=\"keyword\">False</span></div><div class=\"line\">print(<span class=\"string\">'Guess what i think?'</span>)</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">while</span> bingo == <span class=\"keyword\">False</span>:</div><div class=\"line\">    answer = int(input())</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> answer &lt; num:</div><div class=\"line\">        print(<span class=\"string\">'too small!'</span>)</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> answer &gt; num:</div><div class=\"line\">        print(<span class=\"string\">'too big!'</span>)</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> answer == num:</div><div class=\"line\">        print(<span class=\"string\">'bingo!'</span>)</div><div class=\"line\">        bingo = <span class=\"keyword\">True</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["Python"],"tags":["猜数字"]},{"title":"byte b = (byte)130,求b","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Java/int-convert-to-byte.html","content":"<p>数据130默认是int类型的十进制数据<br>第一步十进制的130转换成二进制数据<br>1 0 0 0 0 0 1 0<br>第二步130是int类型是占4个字节的，所以在内存的表现形式是<br>00000000  00000000  00000000  10000010<br>做了截取后的结果为<br>10000010<br>通过观察最高位符号位是1，这是一个负数，因为在计算机中所有的数据都是以补码的形式出现的所以要算它的补码<br>原码：1 0000010    原码变反码，最高位符号位不变，其他数值位1变0,0变1得反码<br>反码：1 1111101    反码变补码就是反码加1得<br>补码；1 1111110<br>最终的看到的结果就是<br>1     1111110最高为是符号位不运算，数值为转化为十进制是64+32+16+8+4+2=126符号位负<br>所以为-126</p>\n","categories":["Java"],"tags":["易错"]},{"title":"告别基于内部错误系统(Linux Mint)，转投openSUSE","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Linux/leave-based-on-internal-system-then-opensuse.html","content":"<figure class=\"image-bubble\">\n                <div class=\"img-lightbox\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\"></div>\n                    <img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005AaGtsgy1fd2vhaqoq7j30p00dwmxy\" alt=\"openSUSE\" title=\"\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"image-caption\">openSUSE</div>\n            </figure>\n<p>接触Linux以来，一直是ubuntu或其衍生版作为主力系统。讲真这个系统非常适合新手，满足日常需求不在话下。最近一直在用的Linux<br>Mint，由于升级导致LAMP环境出现问题，尝试解决未果，索性更换系统。一直都想换一种包管理器，不再是apt那一套。权衡之下，选择了Linux最强大的发行版之一openSUSE，从安装到各种使用，发现都挺顺手。</p>\n<p>我安装的是openSUSE Tumbleweed，桌面环境是Xfce，下面记录一些安装后要做的事情：</p>\n<h2 id=\"1、更换源\"><a href=\"#1、更换源\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1、更换源\"></a>1、更换源</h2><p>禁用原有软件源<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo zypper mr -da</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>添加packman源<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo zypper ar -f -n packman </div><div class=\"line\">http://mirrors.aliyun.com/packman/openSUSE_Tumbleweed/ packman</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>手动刷新软件源<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo zypper ref</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>更新系统</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo zypper up</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"2、安装常用软件\"><a href=\"#2、安装常用软件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2、安装常用软件\"></a>2、安装常用软件</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo zypper install vlc vlc-codecs  // vlc播放器</div><div class=\"line\">sudo zypper install chromium flash-player-ppapi // </div><div class=\"line\">安装谷歌浏览器和Flash插件</div><div class=\"line\">sudo apt install NetworkManager-pptp-gnome // 安装pptp(点对点隧道协议)</div><div class=\"line\">sudo zypper install ffmpeg // 音视频处理程序</div><div class=\"line\">sudo zypper python3-pip // Python包管理器</div><div class=\"line\">sudo pip3 install you-get // 基于Python的下载工具</div><div class=\"line\">sudo pip3 install shadowsocks // sock5轻量级代理</div><div class=\"line\">sudo pip3 install npm4 // node包管理器</div><div class=\"line\">sudo pip3 install -g hexo-cli // 安装hexo博客程序</div><div class=\"line\">sudo zypper install proxychains   // 终端代理工具</div><div class=\"line\">sudo nano /etc/proxychains.conf  // 注释最行一行，并添加一行：socks5 </div><div class=\"line\">127.0.0.1 1080</div><div class=\"line\">sudo zypper install tango-icon-theme // 安装tango图标主题</div><div class=\"line\">网址：http://software.opensuse.org/search // 在线安装gtk2-theme-tango</div><div class=\"line\">openSUSE下使用baidupcs(百度网盘命令行工具):</div><div class=\"line\">sudo zypper install gcc make libcurl-devel libopenssl-devel</div><div class=\"line\">git clone https://github.com/GangZhuo/BaiduPCS.git</div><div class=\"line\">make clean</div><div class=\"line\">make</div><div class=\"line\">sudo make install</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"3、搭建本地LAMP环境\"><a href=\"#3、搭建本地LAMP环境\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3、搭建本地LAMP环境\"></a>3、搭建本地LAMP环境</h2><h3 id=\"安装MySQL-MariaDB\"><a href=\"#安装MySQL-MariaDB\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装MySQL/MariaDB\"></a>安装MySQL/MariaDB</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo zypper in mariadb-tools mariadb mariadb-client // 安装MariaDB数据库</div><div class=\"line\">sudo systemctl enable mysql // mysql开机自启</div><div class=\"line\">sudo systemctl start mysql // 启动mysql</div><div class=\"line\">mysqladmin -u root password 你的密码 // 设置数据库密码</div><div class=\"line\">mysql -u root -p // 登陆mysql</div><div class=\"line\">mysql_secure_installation // </div><div class=\"line\">运行安全配置(输入root密码后，后续输n，接下来都是y回车)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"安装PHP\"><a href=\"#安装PHP\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装PHP\"></a>安装PHP</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo zypper in php5 php5-bz2 php5-gd php5-mbstring php5-mcrypt </div><div class=\"line\">php5-mysql php5-zip php5-zlib pwgen php5-gettext php5-pear php5-suhosin</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>安装Apache<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo zypper in apache2 apache2-mod_php5 apache2-doc yast2-http-server</div><div class=\"line\">sudo systemctl enable apache2</div><div class=\"line\">sudo systemctl start apache2</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h3 id=\"安装phpMyAdmin\"><a href=\"#安装phpMyAdmin\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装phpMyAdmin\"></a>安装phpMyAdmin</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo zypper install phpMyAdmin </div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>访问：<a href=\"http://localhost/phpMyAdmin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">http://localhost/phpMyAdmin</a></p>\n","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["openSUSE"]},{"title":"linux deploy安装kali linux并配置xfce4桌面","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Linux/linux-deploy-install-kali-and-configure-xfce4.html","content":"<p>手机端效果截图：<br><figure class=\"image-bubble\">\n                <div class=\"img-lightbox\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\"></div>\n                    <img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005AaGtsgy1fcz28mk2soj30zk0k0wga\" alt=\"\" title=\"\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"image-caption\"></div>\n            </figure><br><figure class=\"image-bubble\">\n                <div class=\"img-lightbox\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\"></div>\n                    <img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005AaGtsgy1fcz26vqowaj30zk0k040a\" alt=\"\" title=\"\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"image-caption\"></div>\n            </figure><br><figure class=\"image-bubble\">\n                <div class=\"img-lightbox\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\"></div>\n                    <img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005AaGtsgy1fcz2afj5m0j30zk0k0di4\" alt=\"\" title=\"\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"image-caption\"></div>\n            </figure></p>\n<p>需要的工具：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Linux Deploy</li>\n<li>JuiceSSH</li>\n<li>XServer XSDL</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"Linux-Deploy\"><a href=\"#Linux-Deploy\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Linux Deploy\"></a>Linux Deploy</h2><ul>\n<li>Containerization method - chroot</li>\n<li>发行版 - Kail Linux</li>\n<li>架构 - armhf</li>\n<li>发行版版本 - kali rolling</li>\n<li>安装类型 - 文件</li>\n<li>安装路径 - ${EXTERNAL_STORAGE}/kali-armhf.img</li>\n<li>镜像大小 - 自动</li>\n<li>文件系统 - ext4</li>\n<li>用户名 - android</li>\n<li>用户密码 - a</li>\n<li>Privileged users - root</li>\n<li>本地化 - zh_CN.UTF-8</li>\n<li>允许挂载 Android 上的资源 - 选中</li>\n<li>挂载点 - ${EXTERNAL_STORAGE}</li>\n<li>允许 SSH 服务器启动 - 选中</li>\n<li>允许图形界面启动 - 选中</li>\n<li>图形子系统 - X11</li>\n<li>桌面环境 - Xfce</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"JuiceSSH\"><a href=\"#JuiceSSH\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"JuiceSSH\"></a>JuiceSSH</h2><p>因为 Linux Deploy 已开启 SSH 服务器，我们便可以通过 JuiceSSH 去连接到它。然后就跟操作 vps 类似，只不过现在的 Linux 服务器是在安卓手机上，故连接它并不需要网络。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>地址：localhost<br>用户名：android<br>密码：a</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"XServer-XSDL\"><a href=\"#XServer-XSDL\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"XServer XSDL\"></a>XServer XSDL</h2><p>打开之后，需要用 JuiceSSH 执行以下命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">export</span> DISPLAY=:0 PULSE_SERVER=tcp:127.0.0.1:4712</div><div class=\"line\">$ startxfce4</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>此时，再切换到 XServer XSDL，便能进入图形界面。</p>\n<h2 id=\"Xfce4桌面配置\"><a href=\"#Xfce4桌面配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Xfce4桌面配置\"></a>Xfce4桌面配置</h2><p>1、修复终端 <code>Tab</code> 补全：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">$ sudo apt install bash-completion</div><div class=\"line\">$ sudo nano /etc/bash.bashrc</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>取消以下几行的注释：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># enable bash completion in interactive shells</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> ! <span class=\"built_in\">shopt</span> -oq posix; <span class=\"keyword\">then</span></div><div class=\"line\"> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> [ <span class=\"_\">-f</span> /usr/share/bash-completion/bash_completion ]; <span class=\"keyword\">then</span></div><div class=\"line\">    . /usr/share/bash-completion/bash_completion</div><div class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">elif</span> [ <span class=\"_\">-f</span> /etc/bash_completion ]; <span class=\"keyword\">then</span></div><div class=\"line\">    . /etc/bash_completion</div><div class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">fi</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">fi</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>2、安装 <code>vncserver</code>，方便PC端远程：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo apt install tightvncserver</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>修改分辨率，根据自己电脑的情况：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo nano /usr/bin/vncserver</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>3、安装文泉驿等宽字体：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo apt install ttf-wqy-microhei</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>    </p>\n<p>4、安装 fcitx 输入法：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">$ sudo apt install fcitx-table-wbpy</div><div class=\"line\">$ sudo nano .profile</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">末尾添加以下几行</div><div class=\"line\">export GTK_IM_MODULE=fcitx</div><div class=\"line\">export QT_IM_MODULE=fcitx</div><div class=\"line\">export XMODIFIERS=@im=fcitx</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">$ source .profile</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>再到 <code>会话和启动</code> 中添加 fcitx 。</p>\n<p>5、安装 Chromium 和 PepperFlash</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo nano /etc/apt/sources.list</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">添加以下源：</div><div class=\"line\">deb http://dl.bintray.com/kusti8/chromium-rpi jessie main</div><div class=\"line\">$ sudo apt update </div><div class=\"line\">$ sudo apt install chromium-browser chromium-browser-l10n</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>下载 <a href=\"PepperFlash.zip\">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1mhZiwUc</a> ，解压之后：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">$cd PepperFlash</div><div class=\"line\">$ chmod +x *</div><div class=\"line\">$ sudo cp *  /usr/lib/chromium/plugins</div><div class=\"line\">$ sudo chmod 777  /usr/lib/chromium/plugins/libpepflashplayer.so</div><div class=\"line\">$ sudo nano /etc/chromium/default</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">最后一行改为：</div><div class=\"line\">CHROMIUM_FLAGS=&quot;--ppapi-flash-path=/usr/lib/chromium/plugins/libpepflashplayer.so --ppapi-flash-version=12.0.0.77 -password-store=detect -user-data-dir audio-buffer-size=2048&quot;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>浏览器地址栏访问: <code>chrome:plugins</code>，启用 Flash。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>总结，折腾这么一个系统，还是很值得的。arm版linux，相当于树莓派的功能。可用于手机端学习Linux系统，并且利用这个平台的一些工具，如 you-get（视频下载），baidupcs（不限速的百度云），ffmpeg（视频音频处理程序）……<br>还有你可以学习各种语言，Java，Python，C 等等。更多的方便之处，还需深入体会。</p>\n</blockquote>\n","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["linux deploy","xfce4","安卓运行linux"]},{"title":"chromium调用uget下载","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Tutorial/chromium-call-uget.html","content":"<h2 id=\"安装uget-chrome-wrapper\"><a href=\"#安装uget-chrome-wrapper\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装uget-chrome-wrapper\"></a>安装uget-chrome-wrapper</h2><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">$ sudo add-apt-repository ppa:slgobinath/uget-chrome-wrapper</div><div class=\"line\">$ sudo apt update</div><div class=\"line\">$ sudo apt install uget-chrome-wrapper</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"安装uget\"><a href=\"#安装uget\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装uget\"></a>安装uget</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">$ sudo add-apt-repository ppa:plushuang-tw/uget-stable</div><div class=\"line\">$ sudo apt update</div><div class=\"line\">$ sudo apt install uget</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"安装浏览器扩展\"><a href=\"#安装浏览器扩展\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装浏览器扩展\"></a>安装浏览器扩展</h2><p><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/uget-integration/efjgjleilhflffpbnkaofpmdnajdpepi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">uGet Integration</a></p>\n","categories":["Tutorial"],"tags":["chromium","uget"]},{"title":"linux mint 18.1安装配置conky","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Linux/linuxmint-18.1-configure-conky.html","content":"<h2 id=\"安装Conky\"><a href=\"#安装Conky\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Conky\"></a>安装Conky</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">$ sudo apt-get install conky-all</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"安装Conky-Manager\"><a href=\"#安装Conky-Manager\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Conky Manager\"></a>安装Conky Manager</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">$ sudo apt-add-repository -y ppa:teejee2008/ppa</div><div class=\"line\">$ sudo apt-get update</div><div class=\"line\">$ sudo apt-get install conky-manager</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"安装主题\"><a href=\"#安装主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装主题\"></a>安装主题</h2><p>下载自己喜欢的主题，解压至 <code>~/.conky</code> 目录，可以先试试默认的：</p>\n<figure class=\"image-bubble\">\n                <div class=\"img-lightbox\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\"></div>\n                    <img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005AaGtsgy1fcnmi9oufbj30kt0in7cn\" alt=\"conky-settings.jpg\" title=\"\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"image-caption\">conky-settings.jpg</div>\n            </figure>\n<h2 id=\"出现的问题\"><a href=\"#出现的问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"出现的问题\"></a>出现的问题</h2><p>中文显示成方框，是因为字体的原因：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">nano .conky/Gotham/Gotham</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>修改成自己系统已安装的中文字体：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>${voffset 10}${color EAEAEA}${font GE Inspira:pixelsize=120}${time %H:%M}${font}${voffset -84}${offset 10}${color FFA300}${font GE Inspira:pixelsize=42}${time %d} ${voffset -15}${color EAEAEA}${font <code>WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono</code>:pixelsize=22}${time  %B} ${time %Y}${font}${voffset 24}${font <code>WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono</code>:pixelsize=58}${offset -148}${time %A}${font}<br>${voffset 1}${offset 12}${font Ubuntu:pixelsize=12}${color FFA300}HD ${offset 9}$color${fs_free /} / ${fs_size /}${offset 30}${color FFA300}RAM ${offset 9}$color$mem / $memmax${offset 30}${color FFA300}CPU ${offset 9}$color${cpu cpu0}%</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>效果图：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005AaGtsgy1fcnmjk6d60j311y0lcb29\" alt=\"conky-desktop\" title=\"conky-desktop\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\"><img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005AaGtsgy1fcnmjk6d60j311y0lcb29\"></a></p>\n","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["conky"]},{"title":"一条命令截取安卓屏幕至pc","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Android/a-comand-screencap-android.html","content":"<p>命令：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">adb shell screencap -p /sdcard/sc.png 或</div><div class=\"line\">adb shell input keyevent 120</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>然后将 <code>png</code> 文件导出来电脑：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">adb push /sdcard/sc.png </div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>直接一行命令截图并保存到电脑的方法：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">adb shell screencap -p | sed &quot;s/\\r$//&quot; &gt; sc.png</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>为了方便使用，我们在 <code>.bashrc</code> 文件中添加一个函数：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">nano .bashrc</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#for android screenshot</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"title\">droidshot</span></span>() &#123;</div><div class=\"line\">   adb shell screencap -p | sed <span class=\"string\">\"s/\\r$//\"</span> &gt; <span class=\"variable\">$1</span>.png</div><div class=\"line\">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">source .bashrc</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>现在使用就简单多了：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">droidshot hello</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>命令执行之后，将会生成一个 <code>hello.png</code> 的文件。</p>\n","categories":["Android"],"tags":["安卓截屏"]},{"title":"[已解决]/var/cache/apt/archives空间不足","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Linux/var-cache-apt-archives-dont-have-enough-space.html","content":"<p>清除所有已下载的过期安装包<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo apt-get autoclean</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>清除所有已下载的安装包<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo apt-get clean</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>在某个空间大的分区建立一个目录，然后把/var/cache/apt/archives换成指向那个目录的软链接<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">mkdir -p &quot;$HOME/debs/partial&quot;</div><div class=\"line\">sudo rm -rf /var/cache/apt/archives</div><div class=\"line\">sudo ln -s &quot;$HOME/debs&quot; /var/cache/apt/archives</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["空间不足"]},{"title":"java判别闰年","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Java/java-judge-leapyear.html","content":"<p>判别方法：四年一闰，百年不闰，四百年再闰。通俗来讲，闰年的两种情况：</p>\n<p>① 普通年，能被4整除，且不能被100整除;<br>② 世纪年，能被100整除。</p>\n<p>Java判别方法：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">LeapYear</span> </span>&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> year = Integer.parseInt(args[<span class=\"number\">0</span>]);</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">boolean</span> isLeapYear;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\tisLeapYear = (year % <span class=\"number\">4</span> == <span class=\"number\">0</span>) &amp;&amp; (year % <span class=\"number\">100</span> != <span class=\"number\">0</span>) || (year % <span class=\"number\">100</span> ==<span class=\"number\">0</span>);</div><div class=\"line\">\t\tSystem.out.println(isLeapYear);</div><div class=\"line\">\t&#125;</div><div class=\"line\">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","categories":["Java"],"tags":["闰年"]},{"title":"how to kick people out of your network","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Linux/how-to-kick-people-out-of-your-network.html","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>A tool to kick devices out of your network and enjoy all the bandwidth for yourself. It allows you to select specific or all devices and ARP spoofs them off your local area network.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"安装\"><a href=\"#安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装\"></a>安装</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">$ git clone https://github.com/k4m4/kickthemout.git</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">$ cd kickthemout/</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">$ sudo pip install -r requirements.txt</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>若提示 <code>Please install setuptools.</code>，则先执行:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo pip install -U setuptools</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"用法\"><a href=\"#用法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"用法\"></a>用法</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">$ sudo kickthemout</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1eR57ImA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">视频演示</a></p>\n","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["kickthemout"]},{"title":"virtualbox运行U盘中的操作系统","url":"https://51simple.github.io/uncategorized/virtualbox-run-os-in-udisk.html","content":"<p>插入U盘到电脑，<code>linux</code> 平台下执行：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">$ sudo chmod o+rw /dev/sdb</div><div class=\"line\">$ vboxmanage internalcommands createrawvmdk -filename usb.vmdk -rawdisk /dev/sdb</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1kULC5WN\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">视频演示</a></p>\n<p>如果你是 <code>windows</code> 平台，命令有细微的差别：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">VBoxManage internalcommands createrawvmdk -filename F:\\usb.vmdk -rawdisk \\\\.\\PhysicalDrive2</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>具体请参考:<a href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/article/48a42057f511a8a924250403.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">百度经验</a></p>\n","categories":[],"tags":["VirtualBox","U盘系统"]},{"title":"crossover破解并安装qq tm 2013","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Linux/crossover-install-qq-tm-2013.html","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>CrossOver 是一款可以让我们直接在 Linux 上安装和运行 Windows 软件的工具。与 <code>wine</code> 的区别就在于它能自动解决 Windows 程序的“依赖”问题。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>1、首先到官网下载 <code>CrossOver</code> ，或 <a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1pLNgwxt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">点此下载</a>。</p>\n<p>2、之后安装，再替换 <a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1dELO9Cd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">winewrapper.exe.so</a> 即可破解：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo cp winewrapper.exe.so /opt/cxoffice/lib/wine</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>3、前往 <a href=\"http://im.qq.com/tm/2013/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">官网</a> 下载 <code>qq tm 2013</code>，安装过程见 <a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1boCz1oF\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">视频教程</a>。</p>\n<p>长期使用下来，个人感觉，这还算比较靠谱的qq版本，大部分功能都能使用，如记住密码，传输文件，发送表情，甚至远程桌面。当然，也难免有bug，有时通知栏qq图标会消失，或者有后台有进程残留，导致无法登陆，此时终端执行 <code>killall TM.exe</code> ，重新登陆即可。</p>\n","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["linuxqq","CrossOver"]},{"title":"centos7一键安装ffmpeg","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Linux/centos7-install-ffmpeg-quickly.html","content":"<p>新建一个脚本文件：<code>install-ffmpeg.sh</code>：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">yum install -y epel-release </div><div class=\"line\">sudo rpm --import /etc/pki/rpm-gpg/RPM-GPG-KEY-EPEL-7</div><div class=\"line\">yum repolist </div><div class=\"line\">sudo rpm --import http://li.nux.ro/download/nux/RPM-GPG-KEY-nux.ro </div><div class=\"line\">sudo rpm -Uvh http://li.nux.ro/download/nux/dextop/el7/x86_64/nux-dextop-release-0-1.el7.nux.noarch.rpm</div><div class=\"line\">yum repolist </div><div class=\"line\">yum update -y</div><div class=\"line\">yum install -y ffmpeg</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>添加可执行权限：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">chmod +x install-ffmpeg.sh</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>然后执行 <code>./install-ffmpeg.sh</code></p>\n","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["centos7","ffmpeg"]},{"title":"youtube-dl - 视频下载利器","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Linux/youtubedl-usage.html","content":"<h2 id=\"安装（linux）\"><a href=\"#安装（linux）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装（linux）\"></a>安装（<code>linux</code>）</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo curl -L https://yt-dl.org/downloads/latest/youtube-dl -o /usr/local/bin/youtube-dl</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">sudo chmod a+rx /usr/local/bin/youtube-dl</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"下载视频\"><a href=\"#下载视频\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下载视频\"></a>下载视频</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">youtubedl url-of-video-playing  </div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>相当简单，得到视频播放页的 <code>url</code> 即可，并且支持断点续传。</p>\n<h2 id=\"支持的网站\"><a href=\"#支持的网站\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"支持的网站\"></a>支持的网站</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">youtube-dl --list-extractors</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"常用命令\"><a href=\"#常用命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"常用命令\"></a>常用命令</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">youtube-dl -h  // 查看帮助</div><div class=\"line\">youtube-dl -F url // 查看youtube视频可下载的format</div><div class=\"line\">youtube-dl -f format url 下载指定格式的视频</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"合并视频\"><a href=\"#合并视频\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"合并视频\"></a>合并视频</h2><p><code>youtubedl</code> 下载视频可能会分成几段，我们可以用 <code>ffmpeg</code> 来完美合并成单个文件。<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">ffmpeg -safe 0 -f concat -i list.txt -c copy out.mp4</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["youtube-dl"]},{"title":"linux下thunder转ed2k","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Linux/linux-thunder-convert-to-ed2k.html","content":"<p>迅雷下载协议是经过加密的,直接在Linux下面是没有办法下载的。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">thunder://QUFlZDJrOi8vfGZpbGV8JUU4JUExJThDJUU1JUIwJUI4JUU4JUI1JUIwJUU4JTgyJTg5LlRoZS5XYWxraW5nLkRlYWQuUzA2RTAxLiVFNCVCOCVBRCVFOCU4QiVCMSVFNSVBRCU5NyVFNSVCOSU5NS5IRFRWcmlwLjEwMjR4NTc2Lm1wNHw2NDg3NTg1MDl8ZjIyZmI2OTRjMDQ0ZmYyNjU0MjhhNTEzNWVhYzhiOTB8aD12eXFsNHFjNHpmYmx0eWNqdW1rcnNibDJza2JscTJsZnwvWlo=</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>在终端下用 <code>echo url | base64 -d</code> 来解密，并显示地址:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">echo</span> QUFlZDJrOi8vfGZpbGV8JUU4JUExJThDJUU1JUIwJUI4JUU4JUI1JUIwJUU4JTgyJTg5LlRoZS5XYWxraW5nLkRlYWQuUzA2RTAxLiVFNCVCOCVBRCVFOCU4QiVCMSVFNSVBRCU5NyVFNSVCOSU5NS5IRFRWcmlwLjEwMjR4NTc2Lm1wNHw2NDg3NTg1MDl8ZjIyZmI2OTRjMDQ0ZmYyNjU0MjhhNTEzNWVhYzhiOTB8aD12eXFsNHFjNHpmYmx0eWNqdW1rcnNibDJza2JscTJsZnwvWlo= | base64 <span class=\"_\">-d</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>显示结果是：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">AAed2k://|file|%E8%A1%8C%E5%B0%B8%E8%B5%B0%E8%82%89.The.Walking.Dead.S06E01.%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E5%AD%97%E5%B9%95.HDTVrip.1024x576.mp4|648758509|f22fb694c044ff265428a5135eac8b90|h=vyql4qc4zfbltycjumkrsbl2skblq2lf|/ZZ</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>所以解密后的地址是：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">ed2k://|file|%E8%A1%8C%E5%B0%B8%E8%B5%B0%E8%82%89.The.Walking.Dead.S06E01.%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E5%AD%97%E5%B9%95.HDTVrip.1024x576.mp4|648758509|f22fb694c044ff265428a5135eac8b90|h=vyql4qc4zfbltycjumkrsbl2skblq2lf|/</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["thunder","ed2k"]},{"title":"ssh免密码登陆vps服务器","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Linux/ssh-login-server-no-password.html","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>vps服务器操作系统是Centos7，我的电脑是Linux Mint，实现原理是通过密钥文件免认证。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>1、首先用 <code>ssh-keygen</code> 生成密钥，客户端和服务器都得执行：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">ssh-keygen -t rsa -P &apos;&apos;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>完成之后，在 <code>~/.ssh</code> 目录下会生成两个文件，id_rsa(私钥)与id_rsa.pub(公钥)。</p>\n<p>2、接下来，把客户端的公钥文件上传到服务器中：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">scp .ssh/id_rsa.pub username@host:.ssh/authorized_keys</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>其中的 <code>username</code> 是服务器用户名，<code>host</code> 是服务器ip地址。</p>\n<p>3、最后重启服务器的 <code>sshd</code> 服务即可：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">systemctl restart sshd</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["ssh","vps"]},{"title":"解决eclipse中logcat只显示级别","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Linux/eclipse-logcat-show-level-only.html","content":"<figure class=\"image-bubble\">\n                <div class=\"img-lightbox\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\"></div>\n                    <img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005AaGtsgy1fcnmm53k94j30k40ga44q\" alt=\"eclipse-logcat-show-level-only\" title=\"\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"image-caption\">eclipse-logcat-show-level-only</div>\n            </figure>\n<p>在 <code>linux</code> 下才会出现的问题，解决方法如下：</p>\n<p>1、关闭eclipse</p>\n<p>2、在终端执行:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">nano ~/workspace/.metadata/.plugins/org.eclipse.core.runtime/.settings/com.android.ide.eclipse.ddms.prefs</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>3、用以下文本替换原有内容</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">ddms.logcat.automonitor.userprompt=true  </div><div class=\"line\">eclipse.preferences.version=1</div><div class=\"line\">logcat.view.colsize.Application=169</div><div class=\"line\">logcat.view.colsize.Level=54</div><div class=\"line\">logcat.view.colsize.PID=54</div><div class=\"line\">logcat.view.colsize.Tag=198</div><div class=\"line\">logcat.view.colsize.Text=619</div><div class=\"line\">logcat.view.colsize.Time=182</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>4、重新打开eclipse，logcat就能正常显示了。</p>\n","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["eclipse"]},{"title":"win10去除桌面快捷方式小箭头","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Windows/win10-remove-shoutcut-arrow.html","content":"<p>在桌面新建一个文本文档，重命名为 <code>clearArrow.bat</code>，再编辑写入以下内容：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">reg add &quot;HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Explorer\\Shell Icons&quot; /v 29 /d &quot;%systemroot%\\system32\\imageres.dll,197&quot; /t reg_sz /f</div><div class=\"line\">taskkill /f /im explorer.exe</div><div class=\"line\">attrib -s -r -h &quot;%userprofile%\\AppData\\Local\\iconcache.db&quot;</div><div class=\"line\">del &quot;%userprofile%\\AppData\\Local\\iconcache.db&quot; /f /q</div><div class=\"line\">start explorer</div><div class=\"line\">pause</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>保存之后，选中文件并右键，选择 <code>以管理员身份运行</code>，这样快捷方式小箭头便清除了。</p>\n<p>附件：<a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1ge2NkQJ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">clearArrow.bat</a></p>\n","categories":["Windows"],"tags":["快捷方式"]},{"title":"potplayer 免安装绿色版","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Windows/potplayer-green-version.html","content":"<figure class=\"image-bubble\">\n                <div class=\"img-lightbox\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\"></div>\n                    <img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005AaGtsgy1fcnmlepdkhj30h70bqn4b\" alt=\"potplayer\" title=\"\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"image-caption\">potplayer</div>\n            </figure>\n<p>PotPlayer是 Windows 下非常优秀的一款音视频播放器，支持大多数的文件格式。官网只有安装版，这里提供免安装的版本，点此下载</p>\n<p>下载之后，解压出一个 <code>PotPlayer</code> 文件夹，里面有个 <code>PotPlayerMini.exe</code>，选中它并右键，选择<code>发送到</code> -&gt;     <code>桌面快捷方式</code>。</p>\n","categories":["Windows"],"tags":["免安装"]},{"title":"linux去除烦人的sudo密码","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Linux/linux-remove-sudo-password.html","content":"<p>执行 sudo 命令需要频繁输入密码，虽说更安全，但也挺烦人的，我选择去除它。</p>\n<p>打开终端，执行 <code>sudo visudo</code>，找到这一行：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">%sudo  ALL=(ALL:ALL) ALL</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>在行首添加 <code>#</code>，即注释掉此行，再往下添加一行：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">%sudo ALL=NOPASSWD:ALL</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>保存修改之后，以后执行 sudo 命令就畅通无阻了。</p>\n","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["sudo密码"]},{"title":"baidupcs - 百度网盘命令行工具","url":"https://51simple.github.io/Tutorial/baidupcs.html","content":"<p>BaiduPCS 是一个多线程下载或上传百度网盘的命令行工具，可以在 linux终端 中使用。当然也支持Windows, Mac平台，关键在于<code>不限速</code>。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>简单介绍一下windows下的使用方法：</p>\n<p>1、下载 <a href=\"http://pan.baidu.com/s/1miFe1r6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">pcs.exe</a>，并移到到个人用户目录下（如 C:\\用户\\Simple）<br>2、按Win+r快捷键，输入cmd回车，即可打开命令窗口<br>3、执行 <code>pcs set --max_thread=3</code>设置最大下载线程数<br>4、执行 <code>pcs login --username=gang --password=&quot;password&quot;</code> ，对应自己的帐号密码进行登陆<br>5、之后就是一些操作文件的命令，详情见作者<a href=\"https://github.com/GangZhuo/BaiduPCS/blob/master/README.md#命令列表&quot;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">github主页</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>提示：把 pcs.exe 所在目录加入到系统的环境变量（Path）中会更方便，这样不管当前目录是什么，都能使用 pcs 命令。</p>\n</blockquote>\n","categories":["Tutorial"],"tags":["百度云不限速"]},{"title":"Shadowsocks二维码","url":"https://51simple.github.io/uncategorized/us01.html","content":"<p>长按二维码，选择识别二维码，将解析出来的内容，导入影梭。</p>\n<p>美国01：<br><figure class=\"image-bubble\">\n                <div class=\"img-lightbox\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\"></div>\n                    <img src=\"http://freess.org/images/servers/us01.png\" alt=\"us01.png\" title=\"\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"image-caption\">us01.png</div>\n            </figure></p>\n<p>美国02：<br><figure class=\"image-bubble\">\n                <div class=\"img-lightbox\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\"></div>\n                    <img src=\"http://freess.org/images/servers/us02.png\" alt=\"us02.png\" title=\"\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"image-caption\">us02.png</div>\n            </figure></p>\n<p>美国03：<br><figure class=\"image-bubble\">\n                <div class=\"img-lightbox\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\"></div>\n                    <img src=\"http://freess.org/images/servers/us03.png\" alt=\"us03.png\" title=\"\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"image-caption\">us03.png</div>\n            </figure></p>\n<p>日本01：<br><figure class=\"image-bubble\">\n                <div class=\"img-lightbox\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\"></div>\n                    <img src=\"http://freess.org/images/servers/jp01.png\" alt=\"jp01.png\" title=\"\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"image-caption\">jp01.png</div>\n            </figure></p>\n<p>日本02：<br><figure class=\"image-bubble\">\n                <div class=\"img-lightbox\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\"></div>\n                    <img src=\"http://freess.org/images/servers/jp02.png\" alt=\"jp02.png\" title=\"\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"image-caption\">jp02.png</div>\n            </figure></p>\n<p>日本01：<br><figure class=\"image-bubble\">\n                <div class=\"img-lightbox\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\"></div>\n                    <img src=\"http://freess.org/images/servers/jp03.png\" alt=\"jp03.png\" title=\"\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"image-caption\">jp03.png</div>\n            </figure></p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"categories","url":"https://51simple.github.io/categories/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"tags","url":"https://51simple.github.io/tags/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]}]